<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0"
         xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
         xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd">
    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
    <groupId>tv.danmaku.ijk</groupId>
    <artifactId>ijkplayer</artifactId>
    <version>0.8.8-ff7.1.1-20260602</version>
    <packaging>aar</packaging>
    <description>ShikinChen/ijkplayer-android (ijk0.8.8--ff7.1) + FFmpeg 7.1.1 精简 VOD mp4/HLS 构建，arm64-v8a + armeabi-v7a。相对 0.8.8-ff7.1.1-20260601 的唯一改动：cmake/ijkmedia/ijkj4a/CMakeLists.txt 把 ijkj4a 由 SHARED 改回 STATIC（静态链进 libijkplayer.so），修复独立 libijkj4a.so 导致 mNativeMediaPlayer jfieldID 为 NULL 的 IJK 启动崩溃（对齐 fijkplayer / 官方 bilibili 的 j4a 静态链结构）。FFmpeg/OpenSSL .a 复用既有缓存，仅重链 JNI 层；链接保留 -Wl,-Bsymbolic 避免 FFmpeg aarch64 tx_float 文本重定位。Vendored for niuma_player. 见 android/scripts/compile/VERSIONS.lock。</description>
</project>
